https://github.com/exceljs/exceljs/blob/5bed18b45e824f409b08456b59b87430ded023ab/lib/doc/worksheet.js#L794-L810

https://github.com/exceljs/exceljs/blob/5bed18b45e824f409b08456b59b87430ded023ab/lib/doc/table.js#L69-L79

It seems to me that the getTable and removeTable are also broken because of this issue.

Possible fix, not sure if things will break, **this should be thoroughly tested**:
```js
addTable(model) {
  const instance = new Table(this, model);
  const { table ) = instance;
  this.tables[model.name] = table;
  return table;
}
```
